{"tid":208943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆乳鐵騎現身街頭","createTime":"2017-04-20T00:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T02:00:31.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b755efddb2fb42871110c814640992f63acb8387","tid":208943,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T00:00:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2017/04/18/4/4191cae0f10f866e2e2883e5236a2dd3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F4%2F4191cae0f10f866e2e2883e5236a2dd3.jpg&h=76093c56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2017/04/18/4/4b38d9cd3e25ed6392737800be29f7ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F4%2F4b38d9cd3e25ed6392737800be29f7ef.jpg&h=e402040a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2017/04/18/a/a5f2eae4813bcfddd94ffc26c4a29cf4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2Fa%2Fa5f2eae4813bcfddd94ffc26c4a29cf4.jpg&h=a96e1c17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2017/04/18/9/937758b77b561e9e6ebde4a4716cdc9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F9%2F937758b77b561e9e6ebde4a4716cdc9c.jpg&h=60e5d97f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相信去過台灣旅行嘅人都知道，當地幾乎所有人都識得揸電單車，好多時馬路上都會有一大班「鐵騎士」，最近當地網上就流傳一位「惹火司機」，佢除咗擁有修長美腿外，上圍 cup 數亦非常傲人，更厲害嘅係，網上有人話呢位「辣媽」已經 60 歲！<br />\n<br />\n從網上流出嘅照片可見，呢位「辣媽」鍾意穿著短褲或短裙，並配上絲襪，露出修長美腿，除咗一對美腿非常吸睛外，呢位媽媽上圍亦幾乎「逼爆」，有網民直言「好大的凶器」。「辣媽鐵騎」相片流出後，隨即引起網民熱議，有網民就話呢位「辣媽」過去都多次成為網上熱話，更有人佢喺台南非常出名，相傳佢係越南人，而且已經年近六十歲，令一眾網民大感詫異。<br />\n<br />\n不過根據台灣《蘋果日報》報道，就話呢位「辣媽」其實係緬甸人，雙腿的確比較修長，其真實年齡則未有六十歲咁誇張。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://sina.com.hk/news/article/20170418/0/1/1/%E8%BE%A3%E5%AA%BD%E9%90%B5%E9%A8%8E-%E7%88%86%E4%B9%B3%E9%90%B5%E9%A8%8E%E7%8F%BE%E8%BA%AB%E8%A1%97%E9%A0%AD-%E7%B6%B2%E5